_components._string:
2048 is an easy and fun 
puzzle game.
It is played on a 4x4 grid 
using the arrows 
or W, A, S, D keys 
alternatively.
This game is mobile compatible
 and you can play it 
on any device - iPhone, iPad 
or any other smartphone.
